itunes:title: MONEY WITH MICHELLE - BUDGETING & SAVING
title: MONEY WITH MICHELLE - BUDGETING & SAVING
description: Daddy Styles aka Tim Draper aka Michelle - is BACK! Money with Michelle is easily one of our most popular episodes and as promised, we decided to make this a monthly installment to help entrepreneurs everywhere get smart with their money! Today we're going into budgeting and saving - how you can be in the know when it comes to your income and Tim's principles for always having money in the bank and never finding yourself in a bind without the money to bail yourself out!
